                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-8">
                        <div class="inline-flex rounded-md">
                            <a href="#" class="inline-flex uppercase items-center justify-center px-8 py-2 border border-white leading-6 font-medium rounded-md text-white font-bold text-sm">
                                Learn more
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="block md:hidden h-56 sm:h-64 md:absolute md:left-0 md:h-full md:w-2/6">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/assets/img/pipe-placeholder.jpg" alt="Support team">
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="relative bg-blue">
        <div class="hidden md:block h-56 sm:h-64 md:absolute md:right-0 md:h-full md:w-2/6">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/assets/img/pipe-placeholder.jpg" alt="Support team">
        </div>
        <div class="relative max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
            <div class="w-5/6 mx-auto">
                <div class="md:mr-auto md:w-2/3">
                    <h2 class="mt-2 mb-6 text-white text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl sm:leading-10">
                        Our history
                    </h2>
                    <h3 class="text-white mb-6 text-lg uppercase">
                        40 YEARS OF EXPERTISE
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-white opacity-75">
                        We're a tight-knit family company operating since 1978, near Newcastle,
                        Australia. Many booms and busts later, we're still here. Our smaller
                        size means we're nimble: addressing your needs as they arise.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-8">
                        <div class="inline-flex rounded-md">
                            <a href="#" class="inline-flex uppercase items-center justify-center px-8 py-2 border border-white leading-6 font-medium rounded-md text-white font-bold text-sm">
                                Learn more
                            </a>
