                    Nam at sem at ligula aliquet placerat. Maecenas nibh diam, pharetra
                    vitae enim non, mattis ullamcorper erat. Quisque id egestas lorem.
                </p>
                <form action="#">
                    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center space-x-6">
                        <input type="text" class="bg-input_bg py-3 px-5 placeholder-black placeholder-opacity-50 rounded" placeholder="Name">
                        <input type="email" class="bg-input_bg py-3 px-5 placeholder-black placeholder-opacity-50 rounded" placeholder="Email">
                        <input type="submit" class="bg-navy py-3 px-16 text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase rounded cursor-pointer hover:opacity-75 transition duration-500 ease-in-out" value="Let's collaborate">
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
